1
00:01:21,100 --> 00:01:26,990
[Love Endures]

2
00:01:27,300 --> 00:01:29,830
[Episode 16]

3
00:01:59,430 --> 00:02:02,280
Guan Chao, thank you.

4
00:02:02,640 --> 00:02:03,920
You always help us out.

5
00:02:04,200 --> 00:02:05,040
It is a small deal.

6
00:02:05,200 --> 00:02:06,510
Grandma, go and get rest.

7
00:02:06,510 --> 00:02:07,310
I can clean them up.

8
00:02:08,750 --> 00:02:09,590
Stop cleaning.

9
00:02:09,590 --> 00:02:10,030
Leave it to me.

10
00:02:10,030 --> 00:02:10,800
No, I can.

11
00:02:10,800 --> 00:02:11,520
I can handle this.

12
00:02:14,000 --> 00:02:14,750
I will pick it up.

13
00:02:43,030 --> 00:02:44,080
Are you all right?

14
00:02:44,520 --> 00:02:45,360
Does it hurt?

15
00:02:51,190 --> 00:02:51,910
Yifei.

16
00:02:52,960 --> 00:02:54,800
See Guan Chao out later.

17
00:02:55,190 --> 00:02:56,710
You should also go
and take a stroll outside.

18
00:02:56,840 --> 00:02:58,470
Don't always stay in the store.

19
00:02:59,750 --> 00:03:00,150
All right.

20
00:03:00,590 --> 00:03:01,470
Thank you, Grandma.

21
00:03:10,240 --> 00:03:12,870
Guan Chao, thank you.

22
00:03:14,400 --> 00:03:15,710
You don't always have to thank me.

23
00:03:16,080 --> 00:03:17,120
Grandma is kind to me.

24
00:03:17,120 --> 00:03:18,560
It's my duty to help her out.

25
00:03:19,190 --> 00:03:21,310
Well, you don't have to come every day.

26
00:03:21,520 --> 00:03:23,590
I can manage by myself.

27
00:03:24,080 --> 00:03:27,800
Do... Do you find it annoying
that I'm in the store every day?

28
00:03:29,560 --> 00:03:30,360
No.

29
00:03:31,910 --> 00:03:33,030
Then, I will go there every day.

30
00:03:34,800 --> 00:03:35,470
Thank you.

31
00:03:41,910 --> 00:03:44,120
Yifei, um...

32
00:03:45,280 --> 00:03:46,630
Hasn't your mom contacted you yet?

33
00:03:54,960 --> 00:03:56,030
Actually, I want to say...

34
00:03:57,240 --> 00:03:58,910
That is, if...

35
00:03:59,400 --> 00:04:02,520
If you don't mind,

36
00:04:03,150 --> 00:04:05,030
I can look after Grandma

37
00:04:05,030 --> 00:04:06,030
and the wonton store with you.

38
00:04:08,960 --> 00:04:10,520
Are you pitying me?

39
00:04:10,870 --> 00:04:12,310
No, I didn't mean that.

40
00:04:13,800 --> 00:04:14,960
What do you mean?

41
00:04:16,160 --> 00:04:16,800
I...

42
00:04:17,510 --> 00:04:18,950
Well, I...

43
00:04:19,190 --> 00:04:19,680
Guan Chao.

44
00:04:20,950 --> 00:04:21,510
Thank you.

45
00:04:29,870 --> 00:04:31,270
Do you have a selection

46
00:04:31,270 --> 00:04:32,390
for the track and field team soon?

47
00:04:33,270 --> 00:04:33,830
Next month.

48
00:04:34,680 --> 00:04:35,600
Let's compete.

49
00:04:35,750 --> 00:04:36,680
Now?

50
00:04:38,310 --> 00:04:39,680
Do you see the tree ahead?

51
00:04:40,600 --> 00:04:42,430
Whoever gets there first

52
00:04:42,430 --> 00:04:43,390
is considered the winner.

53
00:04:43,720 --> 00:04:44,480
It starts now!

54
00:05:26,480 --> 00:05:27,240
You won.

55
00:05:27,680 --> 00:05:28,310
I won.

56
00:05:33,680 --> 00:05:34,360
You will have a prize.

57
00:05:36,560 --> 00:05:37,680
A prize?

58
00:06:05,390 --> 00:06:06,310
I will head home first.

59
00:06:12,630 --> 00:06:13,120
Guan Chao.

60
00:06:15,270 --> 00:06:15,800
Bye.

61
00:06:53,600 --> 00:06:54,720
Huang Yingzi.

62
00:06:54,720 --> 00:06:56,630
Can you stop shaking?

63
00:06:59,120 --> 00:07:00,040
I didn't move a muscle.

64
00:07:00,560 --> 00:07:02,360
You are shaking yourself, okay?

65
00:07:04,560 --> 00:07:05,630
Stop shaking.

66
00:07:05,630 --> 00:07:07,270
I'm going to vomit.

67
00:07:14,750 --> 00:07:15,390
How about this?

68
00:07:16,070 --> 00:07:17,040
Feeling any better?

69
00:07:18,680 --> 00:07:19,600
Much better.

70
00:07:22,070 --> 00:07:24,190
What is with you, Jiang Yi?

71
00:07:24,720 --> 00:07:26,160
You are never a good drinker.

72
00:07:26,160 --> 00:07:27,430
Why did you drink so much?

73
00:07:27,430 --> 00:07:28,510
What for?

74
00:07:38,720 --> 00:07:41,310
Are you aware that you are very heavy?

75
00:07:41,480 --> 00:07:42,240
Don't you feel embarrassed?

76
00:07:42,240 --> 00:07:43,040
A grown man

77
00:07:43,040 --> 00:07:45,040
actually puts his whole weight on me.

78
00:07:45,240 --> 00:07:46,600
You are drunk.

79
00:07:47,000 --> 00:07:47,950
Who is drunk?

80
00:07:48,240 --> 00:07:50,270
I'm not drunk.

81
00:07:50,600 --> 00:07:52,070
I told you I'm not drunk!

82
00:07:52,070 --> 00:07:52,920
What is that loud noise
this late at night?

83
00:07:52,920 --> 00:07:53,270
I'm not drunk!

84
00:07:53,270 --> 00:07:54,120
You are disturbing my night!

85
00:07:56,000 --> 00:07:57,040
I'm so sorry about that.

86
00:07:58,190 --> 00:08:00,560
Are you sure you are not drunk?

87
00:08:00,600 --> 00:08:02,310
Please, I beg of you.

88
00:08:03,360 --> 00:08:04,160
Keep your voice down.

89
00:08:07,950 --> 00:08:09,120
People always say

90
00:08:10,240 --> 00:08:11,950
that we won't remember the booze talk

91
00:08:12,120 --> 00:08:14,190
after waking up?

92
00:08:15,750 --> 00:08:17,720
But I remember everything.

93
00:08:19,240 --> 00:08:20,430
What is it that you remember?

94
00:08:20,950 --> 00:08:22,270
I remember

95
00:08:23,160 --> 00:08:24,190
when I played Truth or Dare

96
00:08:24,190 --> 00:08:26,950
back then,

97
00:08:30,240 --> 00:08:31,430
I lied.

98
00:08:35,790 --> 00:08:37,120
What did you lie about?

99
00:08:39,320 --> 00:08:41,120
Actually, I...

100
00:08:43,790 --> 00:08:44,840
What is that?

101
00:08:48,320 --> 00:08:49,270
Come closer.

102
00:08:56,750 --> 00:08:58,550
Actually, I

103
00:09:03,150 --> 00:09:05,510
want to eat instant noodles.

104
00:09:06,550 --> 00:09:07,360
With sausage

105
00:09:08,550 --> 00:09:09,790
and fried egg.

106
00:09:25,480 --> 00:09:26,750
Be careful.

107
00:09:27,120 --> 00:09:28,150
He is really heavy.

108
00:09:28,270 --> 00:09:29,150
Oh, my. What is this?

109
00:09:29,150 --> 00:09:31,150
Why is he so plastered late at night?

110
00:09:32,600 --> 00:09:33,910
I couldn't find his ID card

111
00:09:34,150 --> 00:09:35,360
to get a hotel room.

112
00:09:35,670 --> 00:09:37,440
So I brought him back here.

113
00:09:37,550 --> 00:09:39,030
What is wrong with his dad?

114
00:09:39,030 --> 00:09:39,910
His son is back.

115
00:09:39,910 --> 00:09:41,080
Why doesn't he come back?

116
00:09:41,390 --> 00:09:43,120
It is no use to say this now.

117
00:09:43,120 --> 00:09:44,440
He already sold his house.

118
00:09:44,440 --> 00:09:45,840
He has no home here.

119
00:09:46,080 --> 00:09:48,270
Go and get him some honey water

120
00:09:48,270 --> 00:09:48,840
to help with his hangover.

121
00:09:49,360 --> 00:09:50,080
I will go now.

122
00:09:51,510 --> 00:09:52,960
Take his shoes off.

123
00:09:52,960 --> 00:09:54,789
I will get him a blanket.

124
00:09:54,789 --> 00:09:55,749
Tonight,

125
00:09:55,750 --> 00:09:57,840
he can make do with it here.

126
00:09:58,870 --> 00:09:59,630
Okay.

127
00:10:00,960 --> 00:10:02,240
I will take your shoes off.

128
00:10:04,200 --> 00:10:04,670
Come.

129
00:10:05,630 --> 00:10:06,790
Hold on.

130
00:10:08,480 --> 00:10:09,630
What are you up to again?

131
00:10:15,360 --> 00:10:16,510
Listen.

132
00:10:16,870 --> 00:10:18,320
I'm not the kind

133
00:10:18,360 --> 00:10:21,240
who takes off shoes
at someone else's place.

134
00:10:22,150 --> 00:10:23,600
Cut your crap.

135
00:10:23,750 --> 00:10:25,440
You were here bared-foot before.

136
00:10:26,000 --> 00:10:26,550
Come on.

137
00:10:27,270 --> 00:10:28,670
Seriously, I don't want
to take my shoes off.

138
00:10:30,320 --> 00:10:30,720
Hurry.

139
00:10:31,270 --> 00:10:32,750
It is not like
I'm taking off your clothes.

140
00:10:32,750 --> 00:10:34,120
She wants to undress me!

141
00:10:34,440 --> 00:10:35,870
Shut up. Come on.

142
00:10:48,480 --> 00:10:49,480
I did nothing.

143
00:10:51,630 --> 00:10:53,150
I just helped him take off his shoes.

144
00:10:53,840 --> 00:10:55,790
Actually, I can do that myself.

145
00:10:56,120 --> 00:10:58,030
That's not what you said just now.

146
00:11:00,360 --> 00:11:01,150
Yingzi.

147
00:11:02,270 --> 00:11:04,480
You two are not teenagers anymore.

148
00:11:05,080 --> 00:11:07,630
Behave appropriately.

149
00:11:09,360 --> 00:11:09,960
That's right.

150
00:11:28,480 --> 00:11:30,320
Are you seeking trouble for yourself,

151
00:11:30,320 --> 00:11:31,080
Jiang Yi?

152
00:11:31,870 --> 00:11:32,870
Instant noodles.

153
00:11:34,910 --> 00:11:35,630
What did you say?

154
00:11:36,080 --> 00:11:38,240
I want instant noodles!

155
00:11:39,720 --> 00:11:40,630
Not so loud.

156
00:11:43,000 --> 00:11:45,790
I want sausage, egg, cheese,

157
00:11:45,790 --> 00:11:46,870
and some vegetables!

158
00:11:50,270 --> 00:11:51,120
I swear

159
00:11:51,390 --> 00:11:53,120
if I ever drink with you again,

160
00:11:53,320 --> 00:11:54,630
I'm a dog.

161
00:11:56,070 --> 00:11:57,510
I will go and make you
an instant noodle.

162
00:11:57,720 --> 00:11:59,120
Stop shouting, please.

163
00:12:02,510 --> 00:12:03,960
No coriander.

164
00:12:17,240 --> 00:12:18,480
What are you looking at?

165
00:12:21,440 --> 00:12:24,390
Your dress...

166
00:12:25,030 --> 00:12:26,550
It looks nice, right?

167
00:12:27,910 --> 00:12:29,120
Yes, it's quite nice.

168
00:12:30,080 --> 00:12:31,030
Did you steal your grandma's dress?

169
00:12:32,840 --> 00:12:34,480
Stop.

170
00:12:34,480 --> 00:12:35,270
The pot

171
00:12:35,270 --> 00:12:36,360
will flip.

172
00:12:40,480 --> 00:12:41,480
You know nothing.

173
00:12:42,000 --> 00:12:43,150
I saved up for a month

174
00:12:43,150 --> 00:12:44,240
to buy this dress.

175
00:12:44,550 --> 00:12:45,670
The latest fashion.

176
00:12:45,870 --> 00:12:47,000
You don't understand. I'm so speechless.

177
00:12:52,720 --> 00:12:53,120
Come over.

178
00:12:53,200 --> 00:12:53,750
I see.

179
00:12:59,480 --> 00:13:00,030
Wait.

180
00:13:00,910 --> 00:13:01,910
I think one is enough.

181
00:13:03,840 --> 00:13:04,750
The national college entrance exam
is approaching.

182
00:13:05,150 --> 00:13:06,150
You need two eggs.

183
00:13:06,480 --> 00:13:07,510
They give you protein.

184
00:13:15,670 --> 00:13:16,790
Look at you.

185
00:13:16,960 --> 00:13:18,480
You are so eager to eat the noodle.

186
00:13:19,000 --> 00:13:20,120
And look at you.

187
00:13:20,120 --> 00:13:21,670
You came to my place to steal crops.

188
00:13:22,600 --> 00:13:23,720
It is almost the exam.

189
00:13:23,720 --> 00:13:24,960
Yet you still have the mood
to play this?

190
00:13:25,320 --> 00:13:26,670
I keep a balance
between studying and enjoyment.

191
00:13:27,600 --> 00:13:29,670
My results have been on a steep rise.

192
00:13:30,080 --> 00:13:31,750
With this improving trend,

193
00:13:32,550 --> 00:13:34,480
I will get into my dream university.

194
00:13:43,480 --> 00:13:44,240
What about you?

195
00:13:44,440 --> 00:13:45,670
Which university do you plan to go to?

196
00:13:49,150 --> 00:13:51,120
I do terribly in my studies.
I don't have high hopes.

197
00:13:51,270 --> 00:13:52,390
Anyway, I won't get into
any universities.

198
00:13:54,870 --> 00:13:57,150
How about we choose the same city?

199
00:13:58,150 --> 00:14:00,440
We can't stay in Hangtian City forever.

200
00:14:03,240 --> 00:14:04,550
Big cities are pretty good.

201
00:14:05,320 --> 00:14:06,320
But the heavy traffic

202
00:14:06,630 --> 00:14:07,870
and confusing roads

203
00:14:08,030 --> 00:14:09,080
are troublesome for me.

204
00:14:10,240 --> 00:14:12,750
We won't be able to meet everyday

205
00:14:13,390 --> 00:14:15,360
if we are in different cities
in the future.

206
00:14:20,150 --> 00:14:21,240
Isn't that good?

207
00:14:21,670 --> 00:14:23,390
You won't be able
to use my laptop every day.

208
00:14:26,270 --> 00:14:28,320
All right, I will do the dishes.

209
00:14:31,000 --> 00:14:31,670
You won't be able

210
00:14:31,670 --> 00:14:33,360
to eat delicious noodles again.

211
00:14:35,750 --> 00:14:36,320
Here.

212
00:14:38,390 --> 00:14:39,150
Try it.

213
00:14:43,200 --> 00:14:45,150
You are quick to sober up.

214
00:14:47,440 --> 00:14:47,910
By the way,

215
00:14:48,390 --> 00:14:49,840
what do you think about Guan's matter?

216
00:14:50,720 --> 00:14:52,000
Well, Guan...

217
00:14:52,910 --> 00:14:54,120
What is your plan for tomorrow?

218
00:14:54,990 --> 00:14:56,470
I have some personal stuff to settle.

219
00:14:56,870 --> 00:14:57,840
What is it you have

220
00:14:57,840 --> 00:14:59,390
in Hangtian City?

221
00:15:00,360 --> 00:15:01,750
Something important.

222
00:15:03,550 --> 00:15:04,240
Fine.

223
00:15:04,390 --> 00:15:05,670
After you finish your things,

224
00:15:05,670 --> 00:15:06,480
I will give you commands.

225
00:15:07,440 --> 00:15:08,030
Okay.

226
00:15:10,910 --> 00:15:12,320
Is the noodle that yummy?

227
00:15:12,510 --> 00:15:14,240
I didn't say that.

228
00:15:15,440 --> 00:15:17,270
Then don't eat it.

229
00:15:18,240 --> 00:15:19,120
Delicious. Absolutely delicious.

230
00:15:19,120 --> 00:15:19,750
I want to eat it.

231
00:15:21,670 --> 00:15:24,030
However, I think this noodle tastes good

232
00:15:24,320 --> 00:15:25,910
probably because...

233
00:15:28,910 --> 00:15:29,750
Because of what?

234
00:15:32,630 --> 00:15:33,790
Because you cooked it.

235
00:15:36,720 --> 00:15:38,390
Scoundrel.

236
00:15:38,440 --> 00:15:39,790
So you were pretending to be drunk.

237
00:16:45,360 --> 00:16:46,200
Let's have a round.

238
00:16:47,790 --> 00:16:48,510
The two of us?

239
00:16:49,200 --> 00:16:50,150
Why? Are you scared?

240
00:16:51,080 --> 00:16:51,550
Bring it on.

241
00:17:01,390 --> 00:17:02,030
Yang Fan.

242
00:17:02,790 --> 00:17:03,200
Yingzi.

243
00:17:03,200 --> 00:17:03,870
Grandma.

244
00:17:04,110 --> 00:17:04,880
You are here.

245
00:17:05,440 --> 00:17:06,160
It must be tough for you.

246
00:17:06,350 --> 00:17:07,030
Not at all.

247
00:17:08,200 --> 00:17:08,880
Have a seat.

248
00:17:08,880 --> 00:17:10,160
I will go and prepare you some wonton.

249
00:17:10,510 --> 00:17:12,160
Grandma, there is no need for that.

250
00:17:12,160 --> 00:17:13,640
I'm not eating today.

251
00:17:13,930 --> 00:17:15,650
It has been some time
since I came back to Hangtian City.

252
00:17:15,720 --> 00:17:18,070
I want Yang Fan
to take me out for a stroll today.

253
00:17:20,070 --> 00:17:20,790
Sure.

254
00:17:21,030 --> 00:17:23,160
Take a walk with Yingzi.

255
00:17:24,270 --> 00:17:25,240
Sorry for the trouble.

256
00:17:27,480 --> 00:17:27,880
Let's go.

257
00:17:33,200 --> 00:17:33,880
Yingzi.

258
00:17:34,960 --> 00:17:36,880
Are you helping Guan Chao
to convince me to go back?

259
00:17:37,680 --> 00:17:38,440
No.

260
00:17:38,680 --> 00:17:40,000
That is his business.

261
00:17:40,000 --> 00:17:40,880
I can't do anything about it.

262
00:17:41,440 --> 00:17:42,550
I want to thank you

263
00:17:42,960 --> 00:17:44,510
for looking after Grandma for us.

264
00:17:45,240 --> 00:17:46,200
After all,

265
00:17:46,200 --> 00:17:47,920
this isn't what you are supposed to do.

266
00:17:50,270 --> 00:17:51,270
(You are still in good shape.)

267
00:17:51,720 --> 00:17:53,070
I thought you had stopped exercising

268
00:17:53,070 --> 00:17:54,160
after working in the office.

269
00:17:55,550 --> 00:17:56,720
I go jogging sometimes,

270
00:17:56,960 --> 00:17:58,070
but I don't play much basketball.

271
00:17:59,270 --> 00:18:01,400
I feel that only my life
is still the same.

272
00:18:01,920 --> 00:18:05,070
Every day, I go to school, exercise,
and play basketball.

273
00:18:06,510 --> 00:18:07,440
No.

274
00:18:08,240 --> 00:18:09,750
You have Yang Fan now.

275
00:18:10,830 --> 00:18:11,720
Thus, I think

276
00:18:11,720 --> 00:18:13,160
you should make some changes

277
00:18:13,550 --> 00:18:14,400
for the sake of her,

278
00:18:14,400 --> 00:18:15,640
even not for yourself.

279
00:18:18,590 --> 00:18:19,440
I did.

280
00:18:20,680 --> 00:18:21,640
She enjoys eating.

281
00:18:22,160 --> 00:18:23,880
So I learned to cook.

282
00:18:24,480 --> 00:18:25,550
She likes watching drama,

283
00:18:25,550 --> 00:18:26,750
and I watch with her.

284
00:18:28,160 --> 00:18:28,920
I have never thought

285
00:18:29,640 --> 00:18:30,349
of doing all these

286
00:18:30,349 --> 00:18:31,919
before.

287
00:18:32,829 --> 00:18:33,789
(You know what?)

288
00:18:35,069 --> 00:18:36,879
I married Guan Chao

289
00:18:37,960 --> 00:18:39,640
because he has been doing things

290
00:18:39,640 --> 00:18:41,110
that are not his responsibilities.

291
00:18:41,880 --> 00:18:43,270
In fact, all of you are the same.

292
00:18:44,160 --> 00:18:45,310
Every one of you

293
