the matter she isn't comfortable with?

326
00:20:11,830 --> 00:20:13,000
As I said,

327
00:20:13,350 --> 00:20:15,350
you do more than you say.

328
00:20:16,000 --> 00:20:17,110
You have been like this
since you were little.

329
00:20:19,160 --> 00:20:21,000
(Don't bother with him.)

330
