600
00:30:43,550 --> 00:30:44,960
What do you think about Yingzi?

601
00:30:45,750 --> 00:30:46,400
Enough.

602
00:30:46,400 --> 00:30:46,880
You...

603
00:30:46,880 --> 00:30:47,590
Don't

604
00:30:47,880 --> 00:30:49,200
shove them up together.

605
00:30:49,310 --> 00:30:50,070
You are so eager

606
00:30:50,070 --> 00:30:51,400
as if our daughter can't find a husband.

607
00:30:51,550 --> 00:30:52,640
Stay out of this.

608
00:30:52,640 --> 00:30:53,830
Don't interrupt.

609
00:30:53,830 --> 00:30:55,160
I'm asking Jiang Yi.

610
00:30:55,160 --> 00:30:57,000
Jiang Yi, answer me.

611
00:30:57,000 --> 00:30:57,880
Madam.

612
00:30:59,070 --> 00:30:59,750
