613
00:31:02,200 --> 00:31:03,110
I need to take this.

614
00:31:10,830 --> 00:31:11,720
Why don't you

615
00:31:11,720 --> 00:31:13,440
set me up with Guan Chao?

616
00:31:14,310 --> 00:31:15,550
Do you hear yourself?

617
00:31:15,550 --> 00:31:17,200
Guan Chao is already married.

618
00:31:17,200 --> 00:31:18,790
You are not

619
00:31:18,790 --> 00:31:19,790
interfering with his marriage.

620
00:31:20,310 --> 00:31:22,400
That is unethical.

621
00:31:22,640 --> 00:31:23,790
You can't be a homewrecker.

622
00:31:23,920 --> 00:31:24,830
This is the bottom line.

623
00:31:28,000 --> 00:31:28,720
I will shut up.

624
00:31:32,550 --> 00:31:34,310
Regarding the character design
of "The Maze",

625
00:31:34,640 --> 00:31:35,880
do you have something to tell me?

626
00:31:38,270 --> 00:31:39,110
No words?

627
00:31:39,830 --> 00:31:40,590
Let me ask you this.

628
00:31:40,720 --> 00:31:41,590
Why did the character

629
00:31:41,590 --> 00:31:42,830
change from an old man

630
00:31:42,830 --> 00:31:44,400
to a high school girl?

631
00:31:44,920 --> 00:31:46,350
If I'm not mistaken,

632
00:31:46,880 --> 00:31:48,790
the high school girl is Huang Yingzi,
right?

633
00:31:49,160 --> 00:31:50,480
How are you going to explain this?

634
00:31:51,860 --> 00:31:53,000
I will settle this.

635
00:31:53,160 --> 00:31:54,070
Jiang Yi.

636
00:31:54,680 --> 00:31:56,310
A commercial game

637
00:31:56,310 --> 00:31:58,310
consists of various costs

638
00:31:58,480 --> 00:32:00,240
and will eventually be launched
in the market.

639
00:32:00,960 --> 00:32:02,680
If you only care about expressing
your own ideas

640
00:32:02,680 --> 00:32:05,000
and even your personal preference,

641
00:32:05,680 --> 00:32:06,510
I don't think

642
00:32:06,510 --> 00:32:08,720
it's what a professional game designer
should do.

643
00:32:10,000 --> 00:32:11,510
Tomorrow, Mr. Gao and I
will be in the office.

644
00:32:12,030 --> 00:32:14,200
We expect a convincing answer from you.

645
00:32:37,310 --> 00:32:39,920
This is caused by circuit aging.

646
00:32:39,920 --> 00:32:40,200
There.

647
00:32:40,200 --> 00:32:41,310
Get me the test pencil.

648
00:32:44,960 --> 00:32:46,960
Grandma, the season is changing.

649
00:32:47,270 --> 00:32:49,200
You ought to bundle up.

650
00:32:49,200 --> 00:32:50,350
Don't catch a cold.

651
00:32:52,310 --> 00:32:54,680
Don't worry,
we will take good care of her.

652
00:32:56,680 --> 00:32:59,200
Guan Chao,
you are so blessed to have her.

653
00:33:00,030 --> 00:33:00,790
Of course.

654
00:33:01,000 --> 00:33:01,880
I know.

655
00:33:06,400 --> 00:33:07,030
Grandma.

656
00:33:07,310 --> 00:33:08,720
We are heading
to the railway station later.

657
00:33:08,720 --> 00:33:10,350
We will visit you again next time.

658
00:33:11,750 --> 00:33:13,240
There is something

659
00:33:13,550 --> 00:33:15,070
I wanted to do.

660
00:33:15,790 --> 00:33:17,270
But I can't recall it now.

661
00:33:18,070 --> 00:33:20,590
I'm old, and I have become forgetful.

662
00:33:20,920 --> 00:33:22,270
Give me some time.

663
00:33:22,720 --> 00:33:24,070
It is fine, Grandma. Take your time.

664
00:33:24,070 --> 00:33:25,110
Tell me when you remember it.

665
00:33:26,310 --> 00:33:26,920
Grandma.

666
00:33:27,510 --> 00:33:29,790
Are you going to give them wonton?

667
00:33:30,400 --> 00:33:32,960
