668
00:33:32,960 --> 00:33:33,590
My memory is so terrible.

669
00:33:33,590 --> 00:33:34,350
I will go get it.

670
00:33:36,030 --> 00:33:37,200
I prepared it for you,

671
00:33:38,400 --> 00:33:39,830
Jiang Yi,

672
00:33:41,200 --> 00:33:43,480
Zhuang Yuan, and Mingyu.

673
00:33:44,680 --> 00:33:45,920
Thank you, Grandma.

674
00:33:46,720 --> 00:33:48,310
I'm glad

675
