683
00:34:55,800 --> 00:34:56,670
What is wrong with instant noodles?

684
00:34:57,440 --> 00:34:58,550
They taste great.

685
00:35:05,280 --> 00:35:07,030
Did Huang Yingzi cook you
a cheese instant noodle?

686
00:35:15,070 --> 00:35:17,550
Jiang, I smell a rat.

687
00:35:17,710 --> 00:35:19,670
You'd better own up.

688
00:35:20,480 --> 00:35:22,110
Out with it. When did that happen?

689
00:35:26,110 --> 00:35:27,110
Two days ago.

690
00:35:27,190 --> 00:35:27,760
Where was it?

691
00:35:28,960 --> 00:35:29,510
Her place.

692
00:35:29,710 --> 00:35:30,630
Her place?

693
00:35:32,800 --> 00:35:35,280
You stayed at hers during these days?

694
00:35:35,550 --> 00:35:36,480
Is that a problem?

695
00:35:36,480 --> 00:35:37,590
You don't think it is a problem?

696
00:35:37,590 --> 00:35:38,840
You stayed at her place, you know?

697
00:35:39,840 --> 00:35:41,710
I have been there before.

698
00:35:42,590 --> 00:35:43,710
Ms. Guo would be doing the cooking,

699
00:35:43,710 --> 00:35:45,070
not her.

700
00:35:47,120 --> 00:35:48,800
It means

701
00:35:49,400 --> 00:35:50,920
that only the two of you
were at home during those days.

702
00:35:52,440 --> 00:35:54,510
But if it was just you two at home,

703
00:35:54,630 --> 00:35:56,760
you could have gone
to Grandma for wonton

704
00:35:56,760 --> 00:35:57,800
or eaten out.

705
00:35:57,880 --> 00:35:59,760
From what I know about Huang Yingzi,

706
00:35:59,840 --> 00:36:01,400
she rarely went back,

707
00:36:01,510 --> 00:36:02,760
and she wouldn't miss the chance

708
00:36:02,760 --> 00:36:04,070
to eat as many Hangtian delicacies
as she could.

709
00:36:05,230 --> 00:36:07,480
There is only one truth.

710
00:36:07,670 --> 00:36:08,510
That is,

711
00:36:09,840 --> 00:36:12,070
it was a deep and quiet night,

712
00:36:12,280 --> 00:36:15,030
and all shops were closed.

713
00:36:18,230 --> 00:36:19,190
It is a great shame

714
00:36:20,190 --> 00:36:21,280
that you are not

715
00:36:21,280 --> 00:36:22,960
a detective.

716
00:36:22,960 --> 00:36:23,480
It hurts.

717
00:36:26,190 --> 00:36:27,190
What else did you do?

718
00:36:27,760 --> 00:36:29,030
Nothing happened.

719
00:36:29,030 --> 00:36:29,710
Impossible.

720
00:36:29,880 --> 00:36:31,590
Your face betrays you.

721
00:36:32,480 --> 00:36:33,150
Zhuang Yuan.

722
00:36:34,000 --> 00:36:34,480
Don't you think

723
00:36:34,480 --> 00:36:36,360
you look exactly the same as your mom

724
00:36:36,630 --> 00:36:38,070
when you're gossiping?

725
00:36:40,030 --> 00:36:41,920
I'm just concerned about you.

726
00:36:42,440 --> 00:36:43,550
Out of the six of us,

727
00:36:44,110 --> 00:36:45,000
Guan

728
00:36:45,190 --> 00:36:46,550
has started a new life

729
00:36:46,550 --> 00:36:47,670
and a family.

730
00:36:47,710 --> 00:36:49,360
Nothing will happen
between Mingyu and me.

731
00:36:49,960 --> 00:36:51,280
But you and Yingzi

732
00:36:51,280 --> 00:36:52,550
are the first couple

733
00:36:52,550 --> 00:36:54,000
I have been shipping
since before.

734
00:36:54,000 --> 00:36:55,480
If you two can't get together,

735
00:36:55,840 --> 00:36:57,320
I won't believe in love anymore.

736
00:36:59,190 --> 00:36:59,920
All the more reason

737
00:36:59,920 --> 00:37:01,960
it is hard for childhood friends

738
00:37:01,960 --> 00:37:03,800
to change their relationship.

739
00:37:03,840 --> 00:37:05,280
There are also six people

740
00:37:05,670 --> 00:37:06,840
in "Friends".

741
00:37:07,030 --> 00:37:08,710
All of them

742
00:37:08,710 --> 00:37:09,760
get along with each other well.

743
00:37:09,760 --> 00:37:10,800
They are good friends.

744
00:37:10,800 --> 00:37:12,190
They only met each other
in their twenties.

745
00:37:12,190 --> 00:37:14,280
It is different from us,
who met at six.

746
00:37:17,510 --> 00:37:18,710
What about that umbrella?

747
00:37:19,070 --> 00:37:20,440
You went through so much to find it.

748
00:37:20,670 --> 00:37:21,800
Why didn't you give it to her?

749
00:37:24,630 --> 00:37:25,710
I can't find a chance yet.

750
00:37:26,000 --> 00:37:28,670
Why do you even need
a right chance to do so?

751
00:37:29,880 --> 00:37:31,000
I will call her for you.

752
00:37:32,360 --> 00:37:33,960
Don't call her.

753
00:37:34,880 --> 00:37:36,230
Also, it is not raining now.

754
00:37:36,230 --> 00:37:37,360
Why give her the umbrella?

755
00:37:38,030 --> 00:37:40,710
Are you sure it has to do with the rain?

756
00:37:43,320 --> 00:37:44,030
Fine.

757
00:37:44,320 --> 00:37:46,000
I will wait for the next rainy day.

758
00:37:46,230 --> 00:37:49,280
I don't want to see this umbrella here
