a few days later.

765
00:39:12,190 --> 00:39:13,150
Do you want to review it again?

766
00:39:13,510 --> 00:39:13,920
Sure.

767
00:39:18,360 --> 00:39:19,110
Zhang.

768
00:39:20,550 --> 00:39:23,190
Why does my name come before yours?

769
00:39:24,110 --> 00:39:25,070
I want it this way.

770
00:39:26,710 --> 00:39:27,280
But

771
00:39:28,230 --> 00:39:29,670
this is your project.

772
00:39:29,670 --> 00:39:31,190
The initiator of this topic

773
00:39:31,190 --> 00:39:32,070
is supposed to put their name first.

774
00:39:32,070 --> 00:39:33,360
Isn't this the rule?

775
00:39:35,150 --> 00:39:35,920
Since when

776
00:39:35,920 --> 00:39:37,590
