777
00:39:39,400 --> 00:39:40,440
Without you,

778
00:39:40,630 --> 00:39:42,670
I would have given up on this project.

779
00:39:43,320 --> 00:39:45,230
So your name should come first.

780
00:39:48,880 --> 00:39:50,670
By the way, I have good news.

781
00:39:51,070 --> 00:39:53,000
Your renewal contract is
in progress now.

782
00:39:53,510 --> 00:39:54,360
Really?

783
00:39:55,360 --> 00:39:57,150
This good news is not only for you

784
00:39:57,150 --> 00:39:58,480
but also for me.

785
00:40:00,400 --> 00:40:01,360
You look so happy.

786
00:40:01,630 --> 00:40:03,480
Aren't you afraid I might surpass you

787
00:40:03,480 --> 00:40:05,840
and take over your position
as the ace journalist?

788
00:40:07,150 --> 00:40:08,000
To be honest,

789
00:40:08,190 --> 00:40:09,320
I'm already tired

790
00:40:09,320 --> 00:40:10,360
of being the ace journalist.

791
00:40:11,070 --> 00:40:13,400
New Perspectives needs a successor.

792
00:40:13,760 --> 00:40:14,670
If I were to choose one,

793
00:40:15,230 --> 00:40:16,280
I hope it is you.

794
00:40:18,960 --> 00:40:20,280
What are you talking about?
You look so happy.

795
00:40:20,280 --> 00:40:20,960
Chief Editor.

796
00:40:21,280 --> 00:40:23,000
Since when did you become so close?

797
00:40:23,000 --> 00:40:24,630
I have been seeing
the two of you together lately.

798
00:40:25,230 --> 00:40:27,480
You will see more of this later on.

799
00:40:28,480 --> 00:40:30,280
No, not for now.

800
00:40:31,400 --> 00:40:32,800
Chief Editor, I want to take a leave.

801
00:40:34,000 --> 00:40:34,480
Why?

802
00:40:35,440 --> 00:40:36,280
What about your work?

803
00:40:37,480 --> 00:40:38,320
I have Yingzi.

804
00:40:38,840 --> 00:40:40,400
After the article is published,

805
00:40:40,710 --> 00:40:42,320
I'm going to take my son on vacation.

806
00:40:42,710 --> 00:40:43,280
Bye.

807
00:40:48,070 --> 00:40:48,760
Huang Yingzi.

808
00:40:49,320 --> 00:40:50,880
You have a lot on your plate.

809
00:40:51,070 --> 00:40:52,110
How is the interview with Ding Ye
coming along?

810
00:40:52,480 --> 00:40:54,320
Are you going to write
a biography of him?

811
00:40:55,510 --> 00:40:56,760
It is almost done, Chief Editor.

812
00:40:56,880 --> 00:40:57,920
You will see the result soon.

813
00:40:58,280 --> 00:40:58,710
Make it quick.

814
00:41:01,150 --> 00:41:02,000
Yes, sir.

815
00:41:06,150 --> 00:41:06,760
This adaptation

816
00:41:06,760 --> 00:41:08,000
is totally unacceptable.

817
00:41:09,710 --> 00:41:10,710
This is the result

818
00:41:10,710 --> 00:41:12,110
