820
00:41:13,510 --> 00:41:15,110
why you find it unacceptable?

821
00:41:17,030 --> 00:41:18,110
Female special forces soldier?

822
00:41:19,880 --> 00:41:20,800
You must be kidding me.

823
00:41:21,000 --> 00:41:22,760
As for the high school girl,

824
00:41:24,360 --> 00:41:25,400
what is good about it?

825
00:41:33,280 --> 00:41:34,510
Or does this character

826
00:41:34,800 --> 00:41:36,230
mean something important to you?

827
00:41:37,280 --> 00:41:38,510
If you can convince me,

828
00:41:39,280 --> 00:41:39,960
I may consider it.

829
00:41:42,360 --> 00:41:44,070
Mr. Gao, I think what Jiang Yi means...

830
00:41:44,070 --> 00:41:46,360
Jiang Yi, to be fair,

831
00:41:46,920 --> 00:41:48,840
let's go back to the nature
of a commercial game,

832
00:41:48,840 --> 00:41:50,280
a special forces soldier

833
00:41:50,550 --> 00:41:52,280
