your personal expression

840
00:42:00,030 --> 00:42:01,480
and business.

841
00:42:08,400 --> 00:42:08,960
Jiang Yi.

842
00:42:10,230 --> 00:42:11,800
You are capable and talented,

843
00:42:12,190 --> 00:42:13,550
