845
00:42:15,800 --> 00:42:16,670
But you need to understand

846
00:42:17,190 --> 00:42:18,590
that you bring this game to the company.

847
00:42:19,190 --> 00:42:20,000
It means

848
00:42:20,320 --> 00:42:21,880
you can't decide this alone.

849
00:42:22,880 --> 00:42:23,440
Jiang Yi.

850
00:42:23,760 --> 00:42:24,550
Tell us

851
00:42:24,550 --> 00:42:25,230
whatever thoughts you have.

852
00:42:25,510 --> 00:42:26,480
We can communicate.

853
00:42:26,480 --> 00:42:27,710
