855
00:42:34,000 --> 00:42:36,230
I'm the prime creator of this game.

856
00:42:36,230 --> 00:42:37,440
I'm the only one

857
00:42:37,440 --> 00:42:39,150
who knows what this game
is supposed to look like.

858
00:42:39,230 --> 00:42:40,400
