00:43:13,400 --> 00:43:15,150
Hello?

865
00:43:15,150 --> 00:43:16,800
Is this Huang Yingzi?

866
00:43:16,800 --> 00:43:17,360
Yes, it is me.

867
00:43:17,360 --> 00:43:18,280
May I know who I'm speaking to?

868
00:43:19,360 --> 00:43:20,190
I'm Chloe.

869
00:43:20,190 --> 00:43:21,320
We met before.

870
00:43:21,710 --> 00:43:23,320
I called you

871
00:43:23,320 --> 00:43:24,710
to ask for your help.

872
00:43:24,710 --> 00:43:25,920
About Jiang Yi?

873
00:43:25,920 --> 00:43:27,110
What has happened to him?

874
00:43:27,110 --> 00:43:29,400
He has a conflict with the company

875
00:43:29,400 --> 00:43:31,230
regarding the character design
of "The Maze".

876
00:43:31,230 --> 00:43:32,280
I would like to seek your help

877
00:43:32,280 --> 00:43:34,150
to persuade him

878
00:43:34,150 --> 00:43:35,550
to communicate calmly with the company.

879
00:43:38,070 --> 00:43:38,800
Okay.

880
00:43:38,800 --> 00:43:40,190
Got it.

881
00:43:52,960 --> 00:43:55,480
Hello, do you know where Jiang Yi is?

882
00:43:55,760 --> 00:43:56,760
In the office, I suppose.

883
00:43:57,800 --> 00:43:58,590
Go straight down that way.

884
00:43:58,880 --> 00:43:59,400
Thank you.

885
00:44:13,920 --> 00:44:14,920
I like you, Jiang Yi.
